---
import Chatgpt from '../components/Chatgpt';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Peter's Website">
    <main>
        <div class="navbar">
            <h3>Peter's Website</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-1">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
            <p>
                A poor 11-th grader in Yanping High School. Interested in Programming (or maybe?)<br/>
                but is fucking bad at it. Self-learning javascript and React, and extremely bad at UI<br/>
                design and css. Likes to play baseball and is a fanatic Houston Astro fan. I fucking hate<br/>
                Mandarin Chinese.<br/>
                Life is all about suffering. Life is boring. Life is truly a struggle.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-2">
                <h1>Astros' Journal</h1>
                <p>
                    My perspective about my beloved 2017 and 2022 world series champion <b>Houston Astro</b> team.<br/>
                    Update every week (if I remember). Including brief review, special players, thoughts about<br/> the week and some intersting things happenning that week.
                </p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-3">
            <h1>Chat-GPT</h1>
            <p>
                Type in something to ask Chat-GPT some questions.<br/>
                comming soon....
            </p>
            <Chatgpt />
    </div>

    </main>
</Layout>

